WEBVTT

00:00:00.346 --> 00:00:02.932
There's no need to push yourself, Lüdaas.

00:00:03.975 --> 00:00:07.730
It must be hard to even sit down
with that wound.

00:00:07.896 --> 00:00:11.942
I permit you to speak
while lying down.

00:00:12.067 --> 00:00:13.943
Y-Yes, sir…

00:00:15.070 --> 00:00:15.987
However…

00:00:17.114 --> 00:00:20.451
if you aren't going to sit,
I suppose you don't need your legs.

00:00:23.411 --> 00:00:26.081
S-Surely you jest…!

00:00:26.789 --> 00:00:30.793
Speaking to Your Majesty…
while lying down?

00:00:31.795 --> 00:00:36.633
I, Lüdaas, would never
show such disrespect!

00:00:42.347 --> 00:00:44.057
I see…

00:00:44.725 --> 00:00:47.811
In that case, let's hear your report.

00:01:08.123 --> 00:01:13.003
{\an8}<i>The blue skies above are hopelessly clear</i>

00:01:13.003 --> 00:01:18.091
{\an8}<i>At my wit's end, I feel a growing frustration</i>

00:01:18.509 --> 00:01:22.930
{\an8}<i>As if to laugh at us hopeless cowards</i>

00:01:23.263 --> 00:01:26.766
{\an8}<i>Countless eyes stare at us</i>

00:01:27.225 --> 00:01:33.106
{\an8}<i>This soul of mine breaks again and again</i>

00:01:33.397 --> 00:01:36.317
{\an8}<i>All I can do is hold it tight</i>

00:01:37.486 --> 00:01:42.533
{\an8}<i>Until the day it turns to ash</i>

00:01:42.783 --> 00:01:45.409
{\an8}<i>I've absorbed all of this sorrow</i>

00:01:45.536 --> 00:01:50.040
{\an8}<i>It has shaped me, painted me</i>

00:01:50.165 --> 00:01:52.876
{\an8}<i>But that's how we got here, right?</i>

00:01:53.001 --> 00:01:57.840
{\an8}<i>One step at a time, just like breathing</i>

00:01:57.965 --> 00:02:00.383
{\an8}<i>These countless scars on my palm</i>

00:02:00.508 --> 00:02:02.385
{\an8}<i>That no longer fade</i>

00:02:02.510 --> 00:02:06.139
{\an8}<i>Are my badge, my story</i>

00:02:06.431 --> 00:02:10.102
{\an8}<i>I faced the fear and shred it to pieces</i>

00:02:10.227 --> 00:02:13.229
{\an8}<i>And let it walk beside me once more</i>

00:02:13.396 --> 00:02:18.110
{\an8}BLEACH: THOUSAND-YEAR BLOOD WAR

00:02:35.210 --> 00:02:36.836
He sure is late…

00:02:37.461 --> 00:02:38.504
Who is?

00:02:38.881 --> 00:02:40.215
What do you mean, "who"?

00:02:40.382 --> 00:02:41.925
I'm talking about Mr. Kurosaki!

00:02:42.383 --> 00:02:44.719
Shouldn't we go help him?!

00:02:44.927 --> 00:02:45.888
There's no need to.

00:02:46.221 --> 00:02:48.639
The enemy's Spiritual Pressure
is already gone.

00:02:49.098 --> 00:02:52.978
Besides, Kurosaki would never lose
to a guy like that.

00:02:53.437 --> 00:02:55.646
I have no intention
of helping him out.

00:02:55.855 --> 00:02:57.024
Are you sure?

00:02:57.024 --> 00:02:58.400
'Cause I do.

00:03:01.110 --> 00:03:02.987
What is it, Inoue?

00:03:02.987 --> 00:03:04.156
Nothing.

00:03:04.656 --> 00:03:06.157
I was just thinking about

00:03:06.282 --> 00:03:08.868
how you and Kurosaki
have become such good friends.

00:03:09.828 --> 00:03:13.039
That's what I like about you, Ishida.

00:03:14.540 --> 00:03:17.919
W-What are you talking about?!
Don't tease me like that!

00:03:18.294 --> 00:03:19.253
I'm back!

00:03:19.879 --> 00:03:20.756
Oh!

00:03:20.923 --> 00:03:23.258
Welcome back, Kurosaki!
Are you injured?

00:03:23.675 --> 00:03:25.927
No, I'm fine, but…

00:03:27.554 --> 00:03:30.389
Oh, sorry, that's my Soul Phone.

00:03:31.724 --> 00:03:33.018
Hello? This is Yuki--

00:03:33.143 --> 00:03:34.186
What?

00:03:34.811 --> 00:03:35.687
What is it?

00:03:36.020 --> 00:03:37.230
Oh, umm…

00:03:37.605 --> 00:03:40.651
It's a message for all the squads.

00:03:37.605 --> 00:03:40.609
{\an8}"INCOMING CALL"

00:03:40.901 --> 00:03:44.947
{\an8}"SPEAKER"

00:03:41.610 --> 00:03:42.693
Listen up.

00:03:42.902 --> 00:03:44.487
I'll be giving you a brief summary
of the situation.

00:03:45.112 --> 00:03:48.241
{\an8}DEPARTMENT OF RESEARCH
& DEVELOPMENT – CONTROL ROOM

00:03:45.447 --> 00:03:46.782
Don't ask any questions

00:03:46.907 --> 00:03:47.949
and follow what I say
the first time around.

00:03:48.366 --> 00:03:49.116
{\an8}"TRANSMITTING"

00:03:49.408 --> 00:03:51.203
57 minutes ago,

00:03:51.328 --> 00:03:54.288
seven unidentified individuals
infiltrated the Squad 1 office.

00:03:54.413 --> 00:03:56.082
52 minutes ago, they retreated.

00:03:56.082 --> 00:03:59.169
One squad member was killed,
but the Head Captain is safe.

00:03:59.877 --> 00:04:00.920
Around that same time,

00:04:01.087 --> 00:04:03.966
one unidentified intruder showed up
near Kokuryo Gate,

00:04:04.132 --> 00:04:05.968
where Squad 1 was standing guard.

00:04:06.884 --> 00:04:11.430
All 116 squad members were killed
in the 182-second battle that ensued.

00:04:12.557 --> 00:04:15.685
Lieutenant Sasakibe was
mortally wounded

00:04:15.978 --> 00:04:18.980
<i>…and died in the Squad 1 office</i>
<i>soon after.</i>

00:04:20.774 --> 00:04:21.899
That can't be!

00:04:22.024 --> 00:04:23.776
Isn't Lieutenant Sasakibe the person

00:04:23.901 --> 00:04:26.362
who's been serving under
Head Captain Yamamoto for ages?

00:04:26.779 --> 00:04:28.490
Are you saying that
such a man was killed?!

00:04:29.533 --> 00:04:30.617
<i>Finally…</i>

00:04:30.826 --> 00:04:34.538
<i>The entry and exit routes used</i>
<i>by these intruders are unknown.</i>

00:04:35.079 --> 00:04:38.165
<i>However, the Soul Shield Membrane</i>
<i>surrounding the Seireitei</i>

00:04:38.333 --> 00:04:39.959
<i>doesn't appear to be disturbed.</i>

00:04:40.418 --> 00:04:42.129
<i>So we believe they possess</i>

00:04:42.295 --> 00:04:44.380
<i>a transportation method</i>
<i>that bypasses it.</i>

00:05:19.833 --> 00:05:21.168
I don't like this…

00:05:21.625 --> 00:05:23.502
Guess I'll go patrol the area…

00:05:32.803 --> 00:05:36.682
I…chi…go!

00:05:38.351 --> 00:05:39.644
N-Nel?!

00:05:40.728 --> 00:05:42.021
<i>Super Acceleration!</i>

00:05:47.026 --> 00:05:48.612
Y-You bastard…

00:05:48.903 --> 00:05:50.947
We haven't seen each other
in a while…

00:05:51.072 --> 00:05:52.199
and this is what you do?!

00:05:52.365 --> 00:05:54.576
Ichigo…terrible news…

00:05:56.036 --> 00:05:58.913
Help us…Ichigo…

00:05:59.372 --> 00:06:00.790
It's Hueco Mundo…

00:06:00.956 --> 00:06:02.166
Hueco Mundo is--!

00:06:04.086 --> 00:06:05.127
Five days, huh?

00:06:05.379 --> 00:06:06.754
Yes, Your Majesty…!

00:06:06.922 --> 00:06:08.589
That is just about enough time

00:06:08.714 --> 00:06:11.927
for us and the Soul Society
to prepare for battle--

00:06:11.927 --> 00:06:13.302
That's in the future.

00:06:13.427 --> 00:06:14.387
Huh?

00:06:14.553 --> 00:06:16.555
Two days ago,

00:06:16.680 --> 00:06:19.475
when you went out to scout
the border intensity level…

00:06:19.600 --> 00:06:21.228
you stated that if we let things
continue to progress as is,

00:06:21.353 --> 00:06:23.980
the Soul Society and
the World of the Living

00:06:23.980 --> 00:06:28.610
would collapse in the near future
due to an imbalance of souls…

00:06:28.735 --> 00:06:30.612
Isn't that right?

00:06:31.071 --> 00:06:33.156
Lüdaas Friegen…

00:06:34.074 --> 00:06:38.786
Are you, who stands before me
right now, a prophet?

00:06:38.954 --> 00:06:40.956
Huh? Well, um…

00:06:41.372 --> 00:06:42.833
Answer me.

00:06:42.915 --> 00:06:47.336
I'm asking if you are a prophet.

00:06:47.670 --> 00:06:49.880
Um… No…I'm not…

00:06:50.132 --> 00:06:53.802
Then why do you talk about
the distant future?

00:06:54.552 --> 00:06:58.055
I want to hear about the present.

00:07:01.100 --> 00:07:02.144
Ebern…

00:07:02.269 --> 00:07:03.519
Y-Yes?

00:07:03.894 --> 00:07:08.108
There is nothing about you
worthy of praise or punishment.

00:07:08.774 --> 00:07:12.987
You were sufficient to keep
Ichigo Kurosaki at bay.

00:07:13.028 --> 00:07:15.990
Oh… Th-Thank you very much!

00:07:17.117 --> 00:07:19.744
Your job is done.

00:07:19.995 --> 00:07:23.165
You shall become the foundation
towards peace.

00:07:26.459 --> 00:07:27.961
You're fine with that?

00:07:28.252 --> 00:07:29.420
About what?

00:07:29.713 --> 00:07:32.882
I thought Arrancar soldiers were
valuable assets

00:07:33.048 --> 00:07:34.468
that did not require combat training…

00:07:35.343 --> 00:07:36.552
It matters not.

00:07:37.345 --> 00:07:41.391
We can just get another Arrancar.

00:07:45.896 --> 00:07:47.564
Hueco Mundo…

00:07:47.730 --> 00:07:50.108
is already <i>my</i> domain.

00:07:50.901 --> 00:07:53.944
It is but one of the many
foundation stones

00:07:54.069 --> 00:07:57.072
towards invading the Soul Society.

00:07:57.865 --> 00:07:58.949
Hueco Mundo?

00:07:59.242 --> 00:08:01.036
What's going on, Nel?

00:08:01.036 --> 00:08:03.079
What do you mean by
Hueco Mundo being attacked?

00:08:03.454 --> 00:08:04.915
By whom?!

00:08:07.083 --> 00:08:08.584
<i>Super Acceleration!</i>

00:08:09.752 --> 00:08:13.005
I tried to hide my presence until
the very last moment before I struck!

00:08:13.214 --> 00:08:16.259
The fact that you can dodge that
is quite impressive, Ichigo Kurosaki!

00:08:16.384 --> 00:08:17.552
Whoops!

00:08:17.677 --> 00:08:20.304
You can't tell who I am
from just my lower body…

00:08:20.429 --> 00:08:21.972
I shall reveal it to you!
I am…!

00:08:22.097 --> 00:08:23.350
Pesche, right?

00:08:29.188 --> 00:08:32.024
{\an8}THE SEIREITEI – CREMATORIUM

00:09:08.019 --> 00:09:09.019
Light the fire…

00:09:11.480 --> 00:09:12.816
Sorry

00:09:12.941 --> 00:09:14.775
for making you come
over here so early…

00:09:14.942 --> 00:09:17.070
That's not a problem…

00:09:17.696 --> 00:09:19.655
But is it true?

00:09:19.905 --> 00:09:21.157
About Hueco Mundo…

00:09:21.783 --> 00:09:22.993
It's true.

00:09:23.451 --> 00:09:25.953
After the deaths of Lord Barragan
and Lord Stark,

00:09:25.995 --> 00:09:30.041
Lady Halibel has been
the ruler of Hueco Mundo…

00:09:31.083 --> 00:09:32.586
But she…

00:10:16.004 --> 00:10:17.087
Run…

00:10:18.965 --> 00:10:19.966
Go…!

00:10:27.932 --> 00:10:29.017
Let's go!

00:10:41.111 --> 00:10:41.946
Lady Halibel!

00:10:44.865 --> 00:10:48.702
We have no idea
why they took Lady Halibel…

00:10:49.037 --> 00:10:51.623
I can't believe
they got Lady Halibel!

00:10:52.331 --> 00:10:54.708
Do you know who they were
or what they were after?

00:10:55.293 --> 00:10:56.503
We have no idea…

00:10:56.794 --> 00:11:00.381
But we're positive that
they've taken several Arrancars.

00:11:00.965 --> 00:11:03.927
And while we were trying to escape,
they cornered us

00:11:04.094 --> 00:11:06.638
and nabbed Dondochakka!

00:11:09.682 --> 00:11:11.183
Ichigo Kurosaki…!

00:11:11.725 --> 00:11:13.852
Please help us!

00:11:16.480 --> 00:11:17.774
Kurosaki…

00:11:18.316 --> 00:11:20.025
I guess I don't even have to ask.

00:11:20.402 --> 00:11:21.903
We're going to go help them, right?

00:11:22.361 --> 00:11:26.533
After everything they told us,
I can't just ignore them.

00:11:27.366 --> 00:11:28.993
Ichigo Kurosaki!

00:11:29.535 --> 00:11:31.120
Ichigo…

00:11:31.955 --> 00:11:33.206
I'm sorry, but…

00:11:33.373 --> 00:11:35.792
I can't accompany you this time.

00:11:36.125 --> 00:11:37.376
Ishida…

00:11:37.961 --> 00:11:39.837
I'm a Quincy.

00:11:40.379 --> 00:11:43.216
I cannot help Hollows or Arrancars.

00:11:44.134 --> 00:11:45.342
I know.

00:11:45.969 --> 00:11:49.722
Quincies exist to destroy Hollows, right?

00:11:50.597 --> 00:11:53.393
I figured you'd say that.

00:11:53.768 --> 00:11:57.980
But you'd sulk about it
if I didn't bother to call you.

00:11:59.106 --> 00:11:59.899
Kurosaki…

00:11:59.899 --> 00:12:00.859
Yeah?

00:12:01.817 --> 00:12:02.818
Be careful.

00:12:03.068 --> 00:12:04.571
Don't worry.

00:12:04.696 --> 00:12:07.365
Even if you're not around,
we'll manage.

00:12:07.990 --> 00:12:08.991
This latest enemy might be--

00:12:08.991 --> 00:12:10.201
My, my…

00:12:10.326 --> 00:12:13.120
Sounds like you guys are having
an interesting conversation.

00:12:14.080 --> 00:12:18.083
Shall I arrange a trip
to Hueco Mundo?

00:12:35.894 --> 00:12:37.144
Your Majesty…

00:12:37.394 --> 00:12:39.855
About the Medallion
we gave to Ebern…

00:12:40.148 --> 00:12:42.192
There are signs that it has been used…

00:12:42.649 --> 00:12:43.777
However…

00:12:47.238 --> 00:12:50.325
How did you happen to arrive
at my place at just the right time?

00:12:50.908 --> 00:12:53.369
Isn't it obvious?

00:12:53.535 --> 00:12:55.245
I was waiting right outside of
your window

00:12:55.370 --> 00:12:56.914
for the perfect opportunity.

00:12:57.039 --> 00:12:58.707
Just kidding.

00:12:57.081 --> 00:13:03.546
{\an8}GARGANTA

00:12:58.832 --> 00:13:03.546
It's hard <i>not</i> to notice two Arrancars
coming down from Hueco Mundo.

00:13:03.671 --> 00:13:05.881
Plus your battle earlier and
the unusual activity in the Soul Society…

00:13:06.006 --> 00:13:10.094
were more than enough reasons
to take caution.

00:13:11.596 --> 00:13:14.974
You've noticed it too, haven't you?

00:13:15.892 --> 00:13:20.562
Kurosaki, everything that's happening
is all connected.

00:13:20.687 --> 00:13:22.981
This is no longer a joking matter.

00:13:25.317 --> 00:13:27.028
All right, time to exit!

00:13:28.613 --> 00:13:30.490
{\an8}HUECO MUNDO

00:13:29.279 --> 00:13:30.405
Come on, come on!

00:13:30.740 --> 00:13:33.576
Don't stop! Keep moving!

00:13:39.039 --> 00:13:40.833
Whoa! We're in the air!

00:13:41.000 --> 00:13:42.335
The enemy is nearby!

00:13:42.501 --> 00:13:44.921
It's usually like this with Mr. Urahara!

00:13:45.046 --> 00:13:46.880
You know me too well!

00:13:46.923 --> 00:13:48.591
We're falling!

00:13:48.924 --> 00:13:49.509
Huh?

00:13:49.716 --> 00:13:50.677
What's the matter?

00:13:50.844 --> 00:13:54.054
Nothing… I thought I heard voices …

00:13:54.889 --> 00:13:56.349
That's impossible.

00:13:56.765 --> 00:13:57.975
Excluding the dead,

00:13:58.100 --> 00:13:59.894
everyone that was there
is with us right now.

00:14:00.352 --> 00:14:01.687
You're imagining things.

00:14:01.855 --> 00:14:02.938
You're right…

00:14:07.902 --> 00:14:10.071
It seems they haven't noticed us.

00:14:10.488 --> 00:14:13.115
Is Dondochakka amongst the captives?

00:14:13.408 --> 00:14:15.451
No, I don't sense
his Spiritual Pressure…

00:14:15.909 --> 00:14:17.703
He's probably in a different group.

00:14:18.078 --> 00:14:20.498
They didn't come back this way

00:14:20.623 --> 00:14:26.504
because they know all the Hollows
and Arrancar here are dead.

00:14:37.849 --> 00:14:39.558
You don't have to see this.

00:14:39.808 --> 00:14:41.519
This is pretty horrible…

00:14:41.727 --> 00:14:42.937
It's no good.

00:14:43.062 --> 00:14:45.565
There really doesn't seem to be
anyone who is still alive.

00:14:45.981 --> 00:14:46.941
I figured not…

00:14:47.317 --> 00:14:49.235
That's how they operate.

00:14:49.860 --> 00:14:51.236
See that?

00:14:51.361 --> 00:14:54.072
That's a flame of condensed
Reishi they use.

00:14:54.698 --> 00:14:57.826
Thanks to that,
even the rocks and sand of Hueco Mundo

00:14:57.869 --> 00:14:59.870
that normally wouldn't burn
were burned away.

00:15:01.163 --> 00:15:04.207
Faced with the powers of people
we had never seen before,

00:15:04.333 --> 00:15:06.878
we lost all direction and means.

00:15:07.754 --> 00:15:09.880
We had no choice but to run…

00:15:10.048 --> 00:15:12.216
Then the guys
who were taken away…

00:15:12.674 --> 00:15:15.094
They might be planning to use them
in their advance guard…

00:15:15.928 --> 00:15:18.889
At worst,
they'll end up like the guys here…

00:15:19.389 --> 00:15:21.893
I see…
Then let's go save them.

00:15:22.018 --> 00:15:23.477
What?! Hold on a second!

00:15:23.602 --> 00:15:25.772
Dondochakka isn't in that group!

00:15:26.022 --> 00:15:27.273
So what?

00:15:27.523 --> 00:15:29.859
We're going to save
Dondochakka anyway.

00:15:29.859 --> 00:15:33.321
What difference is saving
a few more Arrancars before that?

00:15:33.528 --> 00:15:35.865
Well…now that you mention it,
that's true…

00:15:36.157 --> 00:15:38.116
Hey, hold up! Hey!

00:15:38.326 --> 00:15:39.869
Good grief…

00:15:39.910 --> 00:15:42.746
Doesn't he realize those Arrancars
he's trying to save

00:15:42.871 --> 00:15:47.335
were his enemies not too long ago?

00:15:47.710 --> 00:15:48.919
It's so true!

00:15:48.919 --> 00:15:50.672
But you knew that, right?

00:15:50.837 --> 00:15:53.591
That Ichigo would react this way.

00:15:54.049 --> 00:15:57.095
You knew that Ichigo would
do something about it.

00:15:57.511 --> 00:15:59.931
That's why you asked for his help
without hesitation.

00:16:01.224 --> 00:16:03.100
We should go too, Sado!

00:16:03.433 --> 00:16:04.394
Right.

00:16:08.398 --> 00:16:10.817
W-We're going too!

00:16:11.067 --> 00:16:11.900
Okay!

00:16:13.193 --> 00:16:14.778
Get in line!

00:16:14.903 --> 00:16:16.530
Stand with your backs
against the wall!

00:16:16.655 --> 00:16:17.782
Hurry up!

00:16:17.990 --> 00:16:20.868
We don't mind punching
two or three more holes into you!

00:16:21.910 --> 00:16:23.413
{\an8}STERN RITTER "J"

00:16:23.830 --> 00:16:25.873
That guy seems to be their leader…

00:16:26.081 --> 00:16:27.917
Hey, are we really going to do this?

00:16:28.125 --> 00:16:29.711
Perhaps we shouldn't…

00:16:29.836 --> 00:16:30.628
You idiot!

00:16:30.753 --> 00:16:33.047
If we don't do anything,
we'll just end up dead anyway!

00:16:33.715 --> 00:16:35.466
Attention, attention!

00:16:35.591 --> 00:16:36.842
Quiet, please!

00:16:37.134 --> 00:16:39.220
Will you live or will you die?!

00:16:39.345 --> 00:16:44.307
We'll be having a selection competition
for the Hollows and Arrancar!

00:16:44.933 --> 00:16:46.436
I will be…

00:16:46.561 --> 00:16:49.938
stabbing everyone,
starting from the right side!

00:16:49.938 --> 00:16:53.483
So if any of you are thinking,
"No, I don't want to die!"

00:16:53.608 --> 00:16:57.821
Or, if any of you are thinking,
"Please! Let me join you!"

00:16:57.864 --> 00:17:02.785
Then please get down on your knees
and beg like you are licking our shoes!

00:17:03.161 --> 00:17:05.788
All of you here are the chosen few

00:17:05.913 --> 00:17:10.835
who had the luck, wits, and strength
to survive our attack earlier!

00:17:11.169 --> 00:17:14.963
Please don't waste this opportunity!

00:17:15.048 --> 00:17:17.759
If I say I'll join you,
will you spare my--

00:17:18.968 --> 00:17:21.636
No! Of course not!

00:17:21.846 --> 00:17:25.807
Those of you who wish to apply,
must take an entrance exam!

00:17:25.932 --> 00:17:30.645
This selection event will decide who
gets the opportunity to take that test!

00:17:30.813 --> 00:17:33.691
Those of you who don't understand
my explanation will end up…

00:17:33.816 --> 00:17:35.151
Like this!

00:17:35.276 --> 00:17:36.736
Like this!

00:17:37.819 --> 00:17:40.323
– Does the captain really have any intention
– Like this!

00:17:40.490 --> 00:17:41.865
– of bringing back any Arrancar?
– Like this!

00:17:42.075 --> 00:17:43.992
– Not at all.
– Like this!

00:17:44.160 --> 00:17:46.871
He's not interested in Hueco Mundo,
to begin with.

00:17:47.371 --> 00:17:49.164
That is how you'll die!

00:17:53.669 --> 00:17:54.921
– Captain!
– Captain!

00:17:54.921 --> 00:17:58.840
Your response time before
saying "Captain!" was too slow.

00:17:59.092 --> 00:18:00.843
How strange.

00:18:00.968 --> 00:18:03.554
I thought we confiscated
all their swords.

00:18:05.472 --> 00:18:07.892
Lord Aizen's aide, Loly Aiverrne!

00:18:08.101 --> 00:18:10.144
Likewise, Menoly Mallia!

00:18:10.269 --> 00:18:13.815
Don't assume we'd be defeated
by an underling like you!

00:18:20.320 --> 00:18:21.530
Do it.

00:18:21.780 --> 00:18:22.865
– Yes, sir!
– Yes, sir!

00:18:23.074 --> 00:18:23.907
Shall we kill them?

00:18:24.116 --> 00:18:25.201
No.

00:18:25.367 --> 00:18:29.288
His Majesty ordered us to bring him
any idiots with guts.

00:18:29.497 --> 00:18:31.164
Those two have passed.

00:18:31.289 --> 00:18:33.500
Punish them just enough
that you don't kill them.

00:18:34.460 --> 00:18:38.005
However, the fact that
Aizen would appoint

00:18:38.131 --> 00:18:42.300
such weak Arrancars as his aides
shows he's not that great.

00:18:42.801 --> 00:18:45.512
Then again, even Tier Halibel,

00:18:45.637 --> 00:18:47.347
who ruled Hueco Mundo
after the late Aizen,

00:18:47.472 --> 00:18:50.768
was no match against His Majesty,

00:18:50.893 --> 00:18:53.436
so I shouldn't be surprised.

00:18:55.815 --> 00:18:57.441
Hey, I told you not to overdo it…

00:19:02.070 --> 00:19:04.781
May I ask who you people are?

00:19:06.075 --> 00:19:06.951
Huh?

00:19:07.826 --> 00:19:09.996
You dare to speak
poorly of Master Halibel,

00:19:10.121 --> 00:19:12.164
and yet don't know who we are?!

00:19:12.623 --> 00:19:15.500
I guess you underlings
really are clueless!

00:19:15.876 --> 00:19:20.131
It seems you took Master Halibel
while we were away.

00:19:20.298 --> 00:19:22.842
Don't get cocky just because
you defeated

00:19:22.842 --> 00:19:24.676
those self-proclaimed aides to Aizen.

00:19:25.219 --> 00:19:27.012
{\an8}MILA ROSE / SUN-SUN / APACHE –
TRES BESTIA

00:19:36.063 --> 00:19:37.022
What was that?

00:19:37.147 --> 00:19:39.525
It seems like the fight
has already started over there!

00:19:39.858 --> 00:19:42.111
Those Spiritual Pressures
belong to the Tres Bestia!

00:19:42.236 --> 00:19:43.320
When did you get up there?!

00:19:43.528 --> 00:19:45.323
They work directly under Lady Halibel!

00:19:45.489 --> 00:19:47.575
They're super strong and super scary.
And furthermore,

00:19:47.741 --> 00:19:51.037
they're always trying to bump
one another off like cannibalistic beasts.

00:19:51.162 --> 00:19:53.998
The fact that those insane monsters
have arrived means

00:19:54.123 --> 00:19:56.584
that the enemy army is
as good as destroyed.

00:19:57.585 --> 00:20:01.213
– They're terrifying, Ichigo!
– I can't see where I'm going, you idiot!

00:20:07.385 --> 00:20:10.138
What the hell?
Were you talking behind my back?

00:20:11.432 --> 00:20:13.226
You idiot, I haven't said anything.

00:20:13.351 --> 00:20:14.977
More importantly,
wipe away that snot!

00:20:15.560 --> 00:20:17.480
How wonderful.

00:20:17.688 --> 00:20:19.481
You shouldn't be looking away.

00:20:21.067 --> 00:20:22.859
I have a suggestion.

00:20:22.902 --> 00:20:24.569
Surrender.

00:20:25.988 --> 00:20:27.240
Are you stupid?

00:20:31.035 --> 00:20:32.994
You're not as strong as you claim!

00:20:34.372 --> 00:20:36.915
If you surrender
and join our banner,

00:20:37.040 --> 00:20:39.542
you'll be able to work
for His Majesty

00:20:39.669 --> 00:20:43.213
along with your beloved Tier Halibel.

00:20:43.838 --> 00:20:48.134
You will never get to experience
greater happiness,

00:20:48.260 --> 00:20:50.971
now or ever!

00:20:53.932 --> 00:20:55.684
– Don't underestimate us,
– Could you not underestimate us?

00:20:55.684 --> 00:20:57.060
– you damn four-eyed monkey!
– Could you not underestimate us?

00:20:57.185 --> 00:21:00.480
Oh my,
have negotiations fallen through?

00:21:01.022 --> 00:21:03.817
How extremely disappointing.

00:21:04.693 --> 00:21:06.487
{\an8}SQUAD ONE BARRACKS –
CAPTAIN'S MEETING ROOM

00:21:05.403 --> 00:21:06.403
That is the full report

00:21:06.528 --> 00:21:09.030
concerning the infiltration
by the rebel army.

00:21:10.031 --> 00:21:12.826
Thank you, Akon.
You are dismissed.

00:21:13.536 --> 00:21:14.412
Yes, sir.

00:21:18.374 --> 00:21:20.710
Now then, these Ryoka…

00:21:20.917 --> 00:21:23.586
who we tentatively refer to
as the rebel army…

00:21:23.796 --> 00:21:28.843
The invasion by this rebel army who
call themselves the Wandenreich

00:21:28.843 --> 00:21:33.138
is connected to the recent
mass disappearance of Hollows

00:21:33.221 --> 00:21:35.807
in the World of the Living.

00:21:36.599 --> 00:21:39.729
The destruction of a large number
of Hollows in the World of the Living,

00:21:39.811 --> 00:21:42.272
has caused
a great imbalance of souls.

00:21:42.565 --> 00:21:44.900
This could possibly
spell the destruction

00:21:44.900 --> 00:21:48.028
of the World of the Living
and the Soul Society.

00:21:50.030 --> 00:21:52.407
To extinguish souls…

00:21:57.621 --> 00:21:59.874
I'm sure you astute captains

00:21:59.999 --> 00:22:03.169
have already figured it out by now…

00:22:03.836 --> 00:22:06.505
This rebel army is none other than…

00:22:14.512 --> 00:22:16.140
…Quincies.

00:22:29.444 --> 00:22:32.448
{\an8}<i>Everything we had left behind</i>

00:22:32.615 --> 00:22:36.951
{\an8}<i>Our breaths blending as mist</i>

00:22:37.077 --> 00:22:41.332
{\an8}<i>without form or expression</i>

00:22:41.414 --> 00:22:45.586
{\an8}<i>We lie buried as we glare</i>
<i>into the distance</i>

00:22:45.920 --> 00:22:48.547
{\an8}<i>I can't hear anything</i>

00:22:48.672 --> 00:22:51.800
{\an8}<i>I can't seem to cut anything</i>

00:22:51.925 --> 00:22:54.303
{\an8}<i>It feels like I'm sinking</i>

00:22:54.428 --> 00:22:56.262
{\an8}<i>Falling, falling</i>

00:22:56.346 --> 00:22:57.347
{\an8}<i>Touching</i>

00:22:57.472 --> 00:23:00.934
{\an8}<i>Eyes struck wide open</i>

00:23:00.934 --> 00:23:04.188
{\an8}<i>Something no one has ever seen</i>

00:23:04.313 --> 00:23:10.486
{\an8}<i>The furthest reaches are now visible to us</i>

00:23:10.861 --> 00:23:14.490
{\an8}<i>It cannot be undone</i>
<i>and cannot be stopped</i>

00:23:14.615 --> 00:23:18.035
{\an8}<i>This ensuing struggle</i>

00:23:18.035 --> 00:23:22.748
{\an8}<i>Whisk it away beyond</i>
<i>the ends of the earth</i>

00:23:22.873 --> 00:23:24.875
{\an8}<i>Along with our breaths</i>

00:23:25.084 --> 00:23:27.502
{\an8}<i>Take everything</i>

00:23:27.586 --> 00:23:31.132
{\an8}<i>Whisk it away beyond</i>
<i>the ends of the earth</i>

00:23:31.257 --> 00:23:33.174
{\an8}<i>Along with our futures</i>

00:23:33.299 --> 00:23:35.051
{\an8}<i>Along with our world</i>

00:23:36.136 --> 00:23:39.472
{\an8}<i>Something no one has ever seen</i>

00:23:39.597 --> 00:23:45.938
{\an8}<i>The furthest reaches are now</i>
<i>visible to us</i>

00:23:45.938 --> 00:23:47.940
{\an8}<i>Don't you know God's demand?</i>

00:23:48.065 --> 00:23:49.858
{\an8}<i>Don't you know God's demand?</i>

00:23:49.983 --> 00:23:53.528
{\an8}<i>As we tear each other down</i>

00:23:58.159 --> 00:24:01.744
<i>"The soldiers blow their trumpets."</i>

00:24:02.037 --> 00:24:05.708
<i>"Like stars shooting by the ear."</i>

00:24:06.040 --> 00:24:09.377
<i>"The soldiers stomp their feet.</i>
<i>Like thunder in the air."</i>

